('spanish:6-1-celebrities-influencers-and-fame:mcq:7b391494', 'spanish', 'spanish:6-1-celebrities-influencers-and-fame', '6.1 Celebrities, Influencers and Fame', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "Complete: ‘Creo que Rosalía ___ un buen modelo a seguir.’", "options": ["es", "sea", "está", "fue"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "A POSITIVE opinion (creo que) takes the ordinary indicative → es. ‘sea’ (subjunctive) is only needed after a NEGATIVE opinion like ‘no creo que’."}'::jsonb),
