('spanish:6-1-celebrities-influencers-and-fame:mcq:29984d77', 'spanish', 'spanish:6-1-celebrities-influencers-and-fame', '6.1 Celebrities, Influencers and Fame', 'mcq', 'mcq', 1, '{"question": "<span data-say=\"Los famosos sienten mucha presión.\" data-listen></span><br>Listen. What is being described?", "options": ["Celebrities feel a lot of pressure", "Celebrities never feel any pressure", "Celebrities enjoy a little pressure", "Celebrities used to feel pressure"]}'::jsonb, '{"answer": 0, "explain": "‘sienten mucha presión’ = they feel a lot of pressure. B reverses it with ‘nunca’; C weakens ‘mucha’ to ‘a little’; D changes the tense."}'::jsonb),
